{"tid":884100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實歧視有案底個d社會垃圾 罪犯 有咩問題？","createTime":"2018-10-31T10:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T15:36:08.000Z","uid":68626,"like":51,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3516dabbfc7ed7294e7f63f2a9b331ed32156c00","tid":884100,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:40:01.000Z","msg":"首先<br />\n案底本身就係拎黎標籤人<br />\n例如唔可以做主席 難移民<br />\n但係政府就叫人唔好歧視人<br />\n真係笑撚死<br />\n即係政府自己一路歧視緊人<br />\n但係又叫人唔好歧視？<br />\n個班罪犯 以為自己坐撚完監就無事？<br />\n對我地呢班奉公守法既良好市民公平咩？<br />\n根本呢班唔識守法既撚屌就係賤種 要區別對待<br />\n如果唔係整個案底制度把撚咩<br />\n利申 唔見野第一時間懷疑d案底撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae24dd9e24aeff4d2f945eb047fbe58eb6e72665","tid":884100,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:41:34.000Z","msg":"講緊天奇？"},{"pid":"11e8a89425dab6b137884ad25a09a20a22d89f93","tid":884100,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"梁國雄？"},{"pid":"d5b8321167f7779638b3d84e533155723aa8a452","tid":884100,"uid":59328,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"咪就係你地歧視強姦失敗犯，搞到我無得做lalamove，開唔到銀行戶口，差D要自殺呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9088d53efd54aac1e74c3baf595303141c93d7fd","tid":884100,"uid":79481,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"咁依家唔請有案底既人又唔算係歧視<br />\n<br />\n只係政府鼓勵請jie<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果有前科既人搵唔到搵唔到錢<br />\n<br />\n佢會點? 咪好可能拎綜援 或者食番大茶飯<br />\n<br />\n到時候咪又係搞著政府洗錢"},{"pid":"8635810b314183be99167ff997ffe75650418281","tid":884100,"uid":123591,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T11: